  "Title": "data-preserve",
  "Description": "This page demonstrates the <code>data-preserve</code> attribute physically locking DOM memory blocks so they perfectly survive virtual template replacements and routing morphs untouched.",
  "Syntax": "<div data-preserve=\"optional-id\">Non-Reactive Area</div>",
